<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hung Unla. Sem Hitiu !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa thilhih theih leh hatna,
 Muonga semdi'n kuon hitiu;
 Sana buh lak ding a tama,
 Sem dinga kuon ding umlo.

[V2]
 Hung unla, semdi'n kuon hitiu,
 Hun a tawm vaigei ei tai;
 Sana buhvui mantam haw chu,
 Lalpa hatna'n khawm hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Nausen leh damlo gim bangin,
 A umnau gam a he puou;
 A hinnau a muolliem ma hin,
 Hintui a thawn in dawn hen.

[V4]
 3. Hung unla, semdi'n kisa'i tiu,
 Lalpa'n ei sawlna mun ah;
 &quot;Chungleng va leh gamsate ma'n,
 Chieh meng un&quot; Lalpan A tii.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>307</hymn_number>
</song>